Fitness Workouts

Your one-stop guide to a fitter and healthier you!

Follow our group of instructors providing you with easy to follow workouts, from beginners, intermediates to pro sessions!

Our videos cover Stretches, Pilates, Yoga, Aerobics, and much more! 

To use just ask: Alexa, open fitness workouts. 

Why not also check out our Healthy Food Recipes skill? Now available in the Skill Store! Just ask Alexa ‘Open Healthy Food Recipes’
